<paragraph id="IFRS09_BC6.414" base="F33207827"><paranum>BC6.414</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 9"/><data name="paranum" value="BC6.414"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS09_P6937">IAS 39 allowed an entity a choice between:</p><ol id="IFRS09_L0354" base="F33207834" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS09_P6938" base="F33207835">designating a forward contract as a hedging instrument in its entirety; or</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS09_P6939" base="F33207837">separating the forward element and designating as the hedging instrument only the spot element.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>